Croatia sells 50 mln kuna 42 - day T - bills , rate down . Croatia ' s Finance Ministry said on Tuesday it raised 50 million kuna through 42 - day treasury bills . The issue was priced at 98 . 750 kuna with an interest rate of 11 percent , down from 13 percent two weeks ago . Bids equalled the offer , at 7 . 5 - 14 percent . The weighted average was 10 . 96 percent . The bills are payable on November 28 and mature on January 9 . The ministry will next auction 65 million kuna worth of 42 - day T - bills on December 10 . The auctions are not open to foreign investors . - - Zagreb Newsroom , 385 - 41 - 450893 
